---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with the SaaSStatsHub team — general inquiries, press, corrections, partnerships, and DMCA notices. We respond within 48 hours.">
  <article class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 article-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Contact</h1>
    <p>We read every email. Here's how to reach us:</p>

    <h2 id="general">General Inquiries</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about an article, a statistic, or the site in general:
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2 id="press">Press &amp; Media</h2>
    <p>
      If you'd like to cite our data or interview the team, email
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>.
      Please include your outlet and deadline. We can provide:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Original source citations for any statistic we publish</li>
      <li>Higher-resolution versions of charts and infographics</li>
      <li>Written responses to questions about our methodology</li>
      <li>Expert commentary on SaaS market trends (subject to availability)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="corrections">Corrections</h2>
    <p>
      Spotted an outdated number, a sourcing issue, or a factual error? Email
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>
      with:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>The article URL</li>
      <li>The specific data point or sentence that needs correction</li>
      <li>The correct information and its source (if you have it)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We review corrections within <strong class="text-text">48 hours</strong>
      and publish fixes after verification. See our
      <a href="/editorial-policy/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Editorial Policy</a>
      for details on how we handle updates.
    </p>

    <h2 id="partnerships">Partnerships &amp; Data Licensing</h2>
    <p>
      For data partnerships, research collaboration, API access, or bulk data
      licensing, reach out at
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>.
      We do not accept paid placements in our statistics articles.
    </p>

    <h2 id="dmca">DMCA &amp; Copyright</h2>
    <p>
      To report copyright infringement, email
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>
      with the subject line "DMCA Notice." Include the URL of the allegedly
      infringing content and proof of ownership. We respond to valid DMCA
      notices within 72 hours.
    </p>

    <h2 id="privacy">Privacy &amp; Data Requests</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about how we handle your data, or requests under GDPR / CCPA,
      can be sent to
      <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>.
      See our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
      for details.
    </p>

    <h2 id="response-times">Response Times</h2>
    <table class="w-full text-sm my-4 border-collapse">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-text">Inquiry type</th>
          <th class="text-left py-2 text-text">Typical response</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="text-text-secondary">
        <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Corrections (factual errors)</td><td class="py-2">Within 48 hours</td></tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-2 pr-4">General inquiries</td><td class="py-2">2–3 business days</td></tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Press &amp; media</td><td class="py-2">Within 24 hours (if deadline noted)</td></tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Partnerships</td><td class="py-2">3–5 business days</td></tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-2 pr-4">DMCA notices</td><td class="py-2">Within 72 hours</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4">Privacy / data requests</td><td class="py-2">Within 30 days (per GDPR / CCPA)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 id="address">Mailing Address</h2>
    <p>
      SaaSStatsHub is a remote-first operation. For legal correspondence:
    </p>
    <address class="not-italic text-text-secondary mt-2">
      SaaSStatsHub Editorial Team<br />
      sangaypopo@gmail.com
    </address>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
